</section>
<!-- What We Offer Section -->
<section id="offerings" class="py-5 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Opening Statement -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold text-gradient mb-3">Unlocking Global Potential</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-2">Bridging access to opportunity</p>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Facilitating a journey of discovery</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Intro Text -->
        <div class="intro-section text-center mb-5 px-md-5">
            <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                CDSA offers a <strong>world-class, industry-tailored skill training program</strong>,
                and it is <strong class="text-success">absolutely free</strong>. Yes, Free. Gratis. Mahala.
            </p>
            <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                <strong>What exactly is it?</strong> A comprehensive digital skills training program
                partnered with <strong>Cognitive Class (IBM)</strong>, covering AI, Data Science,
                Cloud Computing, Digital Marketing and Web development – paired with industry-relevant soft skills training
                to get you ready for a career or building a business.
            </p>
            <p class="fs-5 text-primary fw-bold">
                If you are looking to develop digital skills, this may be the program for you.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Training Programs Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="section-title mb-3">OUR TRAINING PROGRAMS</h2>
            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Multiple Pathways. One Goal: Employability</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Program Cards -->
        <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
            <!-- Digital Transformation & ICT -->
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="program-card h-100">
                    <div class="program-badge">Digital Transformation & ICT</div>
                    <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5612AQHopR0IsqP_BA/article-cover_image-shrink_600_2000/article-cover_image-shrink_600_2000/0/1704263535002?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=DfjZtO6B-80P22dr7TmsLdnc0oSg_tnKeq5qPb5qXd4"
                         alt="Digital Transformation" class="card-img-top">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="program-duration">
                            <strong>Self-paced, online learning</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            An experiential learning journey covering Digital Transformation,
                            Blockchain, Cloud Computing, and Kubernetes while building a portfolio
                            based on real-world projects. This track is a gateway into the digital
                            economy, learning how to think strategically and implement cutting-edge solutions.
                        </p>
                        <p class="ideal-for">
                            <strong>Ideal for:</strong> aspiring IT professionals, cloud architects,
                            and tech innovators who want to lead digital transformation initiatives.
                        </p>
                        <p class="program-status text-success fw-bold">— Applications now open</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Data Science & Analytics -->
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="program-card h-100">
                    <div class="program-badge">Data Science & Analytics</div>
                    <img src="https://businessanalystmentor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/50000933_s.jpg"
                         alt="Data Science" class="card-img-top">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="program-duration">
                            <strong>Self-paced, online learning</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            An immersive learning journey where students master Data Science fundamentals,
                            Python programming, Data Analysis, and Visualization, while building real-world
                            projects that showcase their analytical skills and readiness for the data-driven economy.
                        </p>
                        <p class="ideal-for">
                            <strong>Ideal for:</strong> aspiring data analysts, business intelligence specialists,
                            and researchers who want to extract insights and drive data-informed decisions.
                        </p>
                        <p class="program-status text-success fw-bold">— Applications now open</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- AI & Machine Learning -->
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="program-card h-100">
                    <div class="program-badge">AI & Machine Learning</div>
                    <img src="https://miro.medium.com/0*3qRFAwF3tLSMuT-_"
                         alt="AI & Machine Learning" class="card-img-top">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="program-duration">
                            <strong>Self-paced, online learning</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            A comprehensive journey covering AI fundamentals, Machine Learning principles,
                            and practical applications, while building intelligent solutions that solve
                            real problems. This track prepares you for the AI revolution, not just learning
                            algorithms, but learning how to build systems that think and learn.
                        </p>
                        <p class="ideal-for">
                            <strong>Ideal for:</strong> aspiring AI engineers, ML developers, and innovators
                            who want to build the intelligent systems of tomorrow.
                        </p>
                        <p class="program-status text-success fw-bold">— Applications now open</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Results Section -->
        <div class="results-section py-5 bg-light-blue-section">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title mb-3">So, does the program "work"?</h2>
                <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Well, the results speak for themselves</p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-center fs-5 mb-5 px-md-5">
                It's not just about learning skills, it's about <strong>well-rounded individuals</strong>
                ready to take on the ever-changing digital world. We help youth level up in mindset,
                confidence, and capability, so they're ready for what's next.
                <strong>And we're pretty good at it too.</strong>
            </p>

            <!-- Stats -->
            <div class="row g-4 text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="stat-number">500+</h3>
                        <p class="stat-label">Applications received since 2024</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="stat-number">150+</h3>
                        <p class="stat-label">Youth currently enrolled</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="stat-number">50+</h3>
                        <p class="stat-label">Program completions</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="stat-number">85%</h3>
                        <p class="stat-label">Skills acquisition rate</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
